1
00:00:00,429 --> 00:00:08,529
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,703 --> 00:00:16,940
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,179 --> 00:00:19,170
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,184 --> 00:00:25,950
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,021 --> 00:00:29,388
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,591 --> 00:00:33,152
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,528 --> 00:00:36,895
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:36,965 --> 00:00:44,394
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,473 --> 00:00:53,609
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,682 --> 00:01:01,714
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:01,957 --> 00:01:08,795
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,864 --> 00:01:16,930
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,239 --> 00:01:25,704
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,780 --> 00:01:27,805
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:50,349 --> 00:01:52,044
Hey! Geez.

16
00:01:55,454 --> 00:01:57,012
Hey, Pervy Sage!

17
00:01:57,222 --> 00:01:59,918
Weren't you going to
watch my training?!

18
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:02,286
I'm researching now.

19
00:02:02,561 --> 00:02:03,755
Do it yourself!

20
00:02:05,531 --> 00:02:09,490
All right, then I'll summon a frog,
a frog so big you'll be shocked!

21
00:02:13,338 --> 00:02:14,600
The Summoning Jutsu!

22
00:02:18,444 --> 00:02:21,675
Hmm? What's wrong
Did a frog appear?

23
00:02:24,683 --> 00:02:26,844
W-Wait a minute!

24
00:02:28,353 --> 00:02:29,945
What part of that's a frog?!

25
00:02:30,022 --> 00:02:32,490
If you don't get serious,
I won't help you!

26
00:02:32,658 --> 00:02:35,889
Shut up! I am being serious!

27
00:02:35,994 --> 00:02:39,691
Then somehow find your Chakra
as if your life depended on it!

28
00:02:39,898 --> 00:02:41,763
That's what I'm doing!

29
00:03:13,198 --> 00:03:13,721
Huh?!

30
00:03:27,412 --> 00:03:28,242
Sasuke...

31
00:03:29,781 --> 00:03:31,373
Hey Sakura!

32
00:03:31,450 --> 00:03:32,109
Huh?!

33
00:03:32,518 --> 00:03:35,078
Sakura! It's about time you wake
and help me over here!

34
00:03:35,387 --> 00:03:37,981
I'm not sleeping!
I'm busy right now!

35
00:03:38,157 --> 00:03:40,990
Yes, yes...
Then when won't you be busy?

36
00:03:41,994 --> 00:03:42,824
Later!

37
00:03:47,833 --> 00:03:50,267
I can't believe it... Geez!

38
00:03:53,739 --> 00:03:59,678
<i>A Feeling of Yearning,</i>
<i>A Flower Full of Hope</i>

39
00:04:02,514 --> 00:04:05,210
Some of you have probably
already heard but...

40
00:04:05,551 --> 00:04:09,544
Gekko Hayate's corpse was
found near Kikyo Castle...

41
00:04:09,821 --> 00:04:11,516
What... Hayate?

42
00:04:12,124 --> 00:04:12,818
No way...

43
00:04:13,492 --> 00:04:14,254
That's ridiculous!

44
00:04:15,627 --> 00:04:17,595
Is the opponent Orochimaru?

45
00:04:17,896 --> 00:04:20,831
No... we shouldn't jump to
that conclusion so easily.

46
00:04:21,934 --> 00:04:25,529
The one Hayate was following
was likely a Sound spy called Kabuto...

47
00:04:26,438 --> 00:04:29,839
Well, it's certain that Orochimaru
is trying to do something but...

48
00:04:30,075 --> 00:04:34,375
So... we'll cancel Chunin Exam
and go after Orochimaru...?!

49
00:04:35,113 --> 00:04:38,480
No, he revealed his identity to Anko...

50
00:04:38,550 --> 00:04:41,178
sending us a threat not to cancel.

51
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:43,311
Not to cancel the Chunin Exam

52
00:04:43,388 --> 00:04:46,516
for which all of the Ninja of
the Alliance have gathered!

53
00:04:47,025 --> 00:04:48,424
What does it mean?

54
00:04:49,394 --> 00:04:53,797
Orochimaru possesses enough power
to take down a small Land on his own.

55
00:04:53,999 --> 00:04:59,335
He's a Ninja that probably
every land has eyes on.

56
00:05:00,539 --> 00:05:02,507
Moreover, he conveniently holds
a grudge

57
00:05:02,574 --> 00:05:04,269
against this Village Hidden
in the Leaves.

58
00:05:05,077 --> 00:05:06,874
Any Land would desire him.

59
00:05:07,012 --> 00:05:08,138
So could it be...

60
00:05:08,313 --> 00:05:10,645
that any Land in the Alliance
would unite with Orochimaru

61
00:05:10,782 --> 00:05:12,613
and betray the Village Hidden
in the Leaves?!

62
00:05:15,554 --> 00:05:20,321
Well, the Alliance Treaty is at
the same level as a verbal agreement!

63
00:05:22,327 --> 00:05:25,296
As was in the former Great Ninja War...

64
00:05:26,698 --> 00:05:27,665
In any case,

65
00:05:28,967 --> 00:05:31,060
there's too little information
right now.

66
00:05:31,303 --> 00:05:33,498
Let's end these unnecessary
suspicions.

67
00:05:34,006 --> 00:05:35,667
We've already dispatched Anbu,

68
00:05:35,741 --> 00:05:38,005
the black ops to each Land
to collect information.

69
00:05:38,310 --> 00:05:40,642
It's dangerous to act carelessly...

70
00:05:41,079 --> 00:05:43,809
That could be what the enemy
is aiming for.

71
00:05:45,183 --> 00:05:46,047
And also...

72
00:05:53,492 --> 00:05:56,256
I trust all of you!

73
00:06:02,768 --> 00:06:04,201
When the time comes,

74
00:06:04,269 --> 00:06:08,069
we'll bring all the powers of Hidden Leaf
Village together and simply fight!

75
00:06:33,865 --> 00:06:34,695
At that time...

76
00:06:37,502 --> 00:06:39,595
<i>Be quiet about this bruise!</i>

77
00:06:47,512 --> 00:06:49,946
<i>Should I have stopped him forcefully...?</i>

78
00:06:54,019 --> 00:06:55,350
No visitors?

79
00:06:55,787 --> 00:06:58,153
That's correct.
I'm sorry but...

80
00:06:58,290 --> 00:07:01,088
I know he's been hospitalized,
but no visitors...?!

81
00:07:01,626 --> 00:07:02,593
What's going on?

82
00:07:03,195 --> 00:07:06,460
We're also not aware of the details so...

83
00:07:12,537 --> 00:07:14,562
There's no use worrying about it here.

84
00:07:24,916 --> 00:07:25,541
Huh?

85
00:07:26,184 --> 00:07:28,084
Should I bring get well flowers?

86
00:07:32,424 --> 00:07:33,356
So pretty.

87
00:07:38,397 --> 00:07:39,386
<i>Oh no!</i>

88
00:07:39,598 --> 00:07:44,968
Oh... How unusual for you to come
by to buy our flowers.

89
00:07:45,504 --> 00:07:48,371
N-Not really!
Why would you care?

90
00:07:49,107 --> 00:07:51,735
Besides, isn't it unusual that
you're minding the shop?

91
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:55,444
<i>I'll choose quickly.</i>

92
00:07:55,847 --> 00:07:58,145
People don't like flowers with
roots when they're in the hospital

93
00:07:58,216 --> 00:08:00,184
since they don't want to
be "rooted" in the hospital...

94
00:08:00,519 --> 00:08:02,885
So cut flowers are fundamental.

95
00:08:03,789 --> 00:08:05,882
W-What are you talking about...?

96
00:08:06,324 --> 00:08:07,655
Playing dumb won't work!

97
00:08:08,126 --> 00:08:10,458
You're going to see Sasuke, right?

98
00:08:13,098 --> 00:08:15,896
Mom! I'm going out for a bit!

99
00:08:16,601 --> 00:08:18,091
I-Ino?!

100
00:08:18,236 --> 00:08:22,070
I won't let you be the first to visit!
I'm going with you!

101
00:08:22,574 --> 00:08:24,701
A get well visit!

102
00:08:26,044 --> 00:08:28,012
<i>Shucks... Ino pig!</i>

103
00:08:30,849 --> 00:08:32,714
I'm taking this flower...

104
00:08:33,118 --> 00:08:34,983
One "rose" of love!

105
00:08:36,354 --> 00:08:37,582
That's so cliché...

106
00:08:38,123 --> 00:08:41,058
Then I'll make mine this.
"Narcissus!

107
00:08:42,027 --> 00:08:44,860
A noble flower that doesn't
succumb to the cold of the winter,

108
00:08:44,930 --> 00:08:47,626
but hopes for the spring and
waits with dignified presence...

109
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:52,267
<i>with the wish for release from</i>
<i>the hospital as soon as possible.</i>

110
00:08:52,737 --> 00:08:55,001
You've gotten pretty knowledgeable.

111
00:08:55,106 --> 00:08:57,006
I told you I wouldn't lose to you!

112
00:08:57,209 --> 00:09:00,372
Oh, yes yes, so one narcissus, right?

113
00:09:00,445 --> 00:09:02,242
Uh... I need two.

114
00:09:02,481 --> 00:09:04,972
Why? One is fine.

115
00:09:05,217 --> 00:09:07,481
No... One for Lee too.

116
00:09:20,732 --> 00:09:21,824
More please!

117
00:09:21,967 --> 00:09:22,763
- Huh?!
- Huh?

118
00:09:23,668 --> 00:09:25,329
Ten orders of <i>kalbi!</i>

119
00:09:30,742 --> 00:09:34,473
You sure can eat.
Just watching you makes me feel ill.

120
00:09:35,247 --> 00:09:36,305
Here you are!

121
00:09:37,415 --> 00:09:38,279
It's here!

122
00:09:41,019 --> 00:09:44,284
This is mine, all right?
Don't eat any of it, Shikamaru!

123
00:09:45,223 --> 00:09:46,520
I won't eat any!

124
00:09:48,793 --> 00:09:51,728
What's going on with you guys,
barbecue in the middle of the day?

125
00:09:52,097 --> 00:09:52,756
- Oh...?
- Huh?

126
00:09:53,131 --> 00:09:54,428
Ino and Sakura...

127
00:09:54,866 --> 00:09:57,858
Shikamaru, shouldn't you be going through
some special training or something

128
00:09:57,936 --> 00:09:59,267
to prepare for the final exam?

129
00:09:59,337 --> 00:10:00,497
I am...

130
00:10:00,972 --> 00:10:02,337
Every single day...

131
00:10:02,874 --> 00:10:04,967
Asuma is so persistent.

132
00:10:07,012 --> 00:10:10,971
Actually, Choji's been joining us
in the special training.

133
00:10:11,216 --> 00:10:12,513
Really?

134
00:10:12,984 --> 00:10:14,645
So you took it on?

135
00:10:14,886 --> 00:10:19,914
Yup! In exchange, he's treating me
to as much barbecue as I can eat!

136
00:10:20,191 --> 00:10:21,783
I see...

137
00:10:22,160 --> 00:10:26,494
Oh, I shouldn't have held on
for the Final Round.

138
00:10:26,765 --> 00:10:28,164
Don't be ridiculous!

139
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:31,228
There are numerous people who
want to participate, but can't!

140
00:10:31,536 --> 00:10:32,366
That's right!

141
00:10:32,837 --> 00:10:33,633
From what I've heard,

142
00:10:33,705 --> 00:10:36,003
they're doing some awfully
difficult things

143
00:10:36,074 --> 00:10:37,769
over at Guy and Kurenai's team!

144
00:10:37,909 --> 00:10:39,843
W-What's that?

145
00:10:40,445 --> 00:10:41,969
Even though we've made
it this far,

146
00:10:42,047 --> 00:10:44,572
to get totally thrashed
wouldn't be very cool...

147
00:10:45,917 --> 00:10:49,751
Aw man, what a drag...

148
00:11:00,899 --> 00:11:02,059
Whatever the circumstances,

149
00:11:02,133 --> 00:11:04,101
we've exceeded
a human being's limits.

150
00:11:04,603 --> 00:11:06,628
So I've used too much Chakra...

151
00:11:08,273 --> 00:11:09,797
Neji, are you all right?!

152
00:11:47,646 --> 00:11:49,170
Summoning Jutsu!

153
00:11:51,816 --> 00:11:53,784
What?! A tadpole again?!

154
00:11:53,852 --> 00:11:56,320
You haven't made
any progress whatsoever!

155
00:11:56,521 --> 00:11:59,718
See how it's bigger
than the ones earlier?!

156
00:11:59,858 --> 00:12:01,883
How the heck should I know?!

157
00:12:12,204 --> 00:12:14,138
So you want to see
Sasuke Uchiha...?

158
00:12:14,906 --> 00:12:16,100
Just five minutes.

159
00:12:16,475 --> 00:12:18,705
I can't allow you to visit
any longer than that.

160
00:12:19,745 --> 00:12:22,805
His body still needs to rest...

161
00:12:23,415 --> 00:12:24,040
Yes...

162
00:12:25,751 --> 00:12:27,844
Sasuke. You have visitors...

163
00:12:28,220 --> 00:12:29,778
Two cute young ladies...

164
00:12:30,222 --> 00:12:30,745
Oh...!

165
00:12:30,922 --> 00:12:31,650
- Huh?
- Huh?

166
00:12:33,458 --> 00:12:35,756
Sasuke, Sasuke?

167
00:12:38,430 --> 00:12:39,556
His clothes are gone!

168
00:12:39,698 --> 00:12:40,392
- What?!
- What?

169
00:12:40,632 --> 00:12:43,624
It's terrible! He's in no condition
to be walking outside yet!

170
00:12:44,136 --> 00:12:45,865
Doctor! Doctor!

171
00:12:47,572 --> 00:12:48,470
Sasuke...

172
00:12:49,641 --> 00:12:50,437
No way...

173
00:12:52,344 --> 00:12:55,245
<i>Sasuke will, without</i>
<i>a doubt, desire me...</i>

174
00:13:00,452 --> 00:13:03,148
<i>Sasuke... Where in the world</i>
<i>have you gone...?</i>

175
00:13:21,873 --> 00:13:24,273
<i>Could cliff climbing be so taxing...?</i>

176
00:13:25,944 --> 00:13:28,845
<i>Damn, my body is sluggish...</i>

177
00:13:29,881 --> 00:13:31,041
<i>Will I make it in time...?</i>

178
00:13:53,438 --> 00:13:54,097
<i>Open!</i>

179
00:14:10,622 --> 00:14:11,350
Huh?

180
00:14:14,226 --> 00:14:14,920
Yo!

181
00:14:16,027 --> 00:14:18,552
Huh... You finally made it here...

182
00:14:25,303 --> 00:14:28,067
We'll search for Sasuke
on our end.

183
00:14:28,406 --> 00:14:32,206
But if you happen to see him,
please contact us.

184
00:14:32,410 --> 00:14:33,274
- We will.
- Yes.

185
00:14:33,678 --> 00:14:35,737
And also... you wanted to see Lee, right?

186
00:14:35,947 --> 00:14:36,641
- Yes.
- Yes.

187
00:14:38,316 --> 00:14:42,650
He's also in no condition to move,
so please make your visit brief.

188
00:14:44,689 --> 00:14:46,179
Lee, you have visitors.

189
00:14:46,892 --> 00:14:48,484
Two cute young ladies...

190
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:49,619
Oh?!

191
00:14:49,694 --> 00:14:50,558
- Huh?!
- Huh?!

192
00:14:51,563 --> 00:14:53,929
Really... even Lee!

193
00:14:54,366 --> 00:14:56,095
Lee! Lee!

194
00:14:56,468 --> 00:14:57,332
Lee...

195
00:14:57,769 --> 00:14:58,360
Huh?

196
00:14:59,271 --> 00:14:59,965
Look!

197
00:15:00,238 --> 00:15:00,829
Huh?

198
00:15:04,576 --> 00:15:05,406
Lee?!

199
00:15:07,445 --> 00:15:08,241
Sakura, let's go!

200
00:15:08,847 --> 00:15:09,472
Okay!

201
00:15:13,885 --> 00:15:16,080
200 one armed pushups...

202
00:15:16,354 --> 00:15:19,585
If I can't do them,
100 one legged squats...

203
00:15:21,860 --> 00:15:23,691
190...!

204
00:15:29,434 --> 00:15:33,734
Lee! Stop it!
Lee! Stop it!

205
00:15:33,805 --> 00:15:36,000
191...

206
00:15:37,042 --> 00:15:38,031
Lee!

207
00:15:38,109 --> 00:15:39,474
Please don't touch me!

208
00:15:41,379 --> 00:15:45,475
Don't... interfere...
with my training...

209
00:15:49,087 --> 00:15:50,384
<i>I need two...</i>

210
00:15:51,289 --> 00:15:54,019
<i>Why? One is fine.</i>

211
00:15:54,459 --> 00:15:56,586
<i>No... One for Lee too...</i>

212
00:16:01,166 --> 00:16:05,603
Speaking of which, Sakura,
did you hear about that Lee?

213
00:16:05,971 --> 00:16:07,700
What? Hear what?

214
00:16:08,273 --> 00:16:10,935
Well, that Lee...

215
00:16:11,509 --> 00:16:15,741
his injuries were serious and
he can no longer...

216
00:16:15,814 --> 00:16:18,078
continue as a Shinobi.

217
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:24,850
195...

218
00:16:29,728 --> 00:16:32,390
196...

219
00:16:34,633 --> 00:16:37,693
197...

220
00:16:40,105 --> 00:16:42,835
198...

221
00:16:46,111 --> 00:16:49,239
<i>I'm...not finished...yet!</i>

222
00:16:52,417 --> 00:16:54,476
<i>There's no value in making</i>
<i>an effort for someone</i>

223
00:16:54,686 --> 00:16:56,483
<i>who doesn't believe in himself!</i>

224
00:17:11,336 --> 00:17:15,830
One... one hundred... ninety... nine...

225
00:17:20,278 --> 00:17:22,906
One... One more...

226
00:17:25,450 --> 00:17:27,247
One more time...!

227
00:17:30,655 --> 00:17:31,485
- Huh?!
- Oh!

228
00:17:32,490 --> 00:17:33,252
Lee!

229
00:17:41,633 --> 00:17:43,794
I'll... go get the stretcher.

230
00:17:43,868 --> 00:17:45,096
Please keep an eye on him.

231
00:17:45,370 --> 00:17:46,132
Yes.

232
00:18:02,954 --> 00:18:04,421
Hey... Ino...

233
00:18:05,056 --> 00:18:05,750
Huh?

234
00:18:06,491 --> 00:18:11,087
Why do boys...
have to push themselves?

235
00:18:18,636 --> 00:18:22,436
Don't ask me that.
I'm a girl you know!

236
00:18:23,608 --> 00:18:24,199
Sorry...

237
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:30,705
The Human... Boulder!

238
00:18:31,449 --> 00:18:33,041
Ninja Art: Shadow Possession Ju...!

239
00:18:33,952 --> 00:18:35,817
<i>Darn it, I don't have enough Chakra!</i>

240
00:18:47,565 --> 00:18:49,123
What's the matter, Shikamaru?!

241
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:50,633
Have you hit your limit already?

242
00:18:50,835 --> 00:18:53,633
Man! What a drag...

243
00:18:53,838 --> 00:18:56,170
All right, Choji!
One more time!

244
00:19:16,194 --> 00:19:17,286
Who brought that...?

245
00:19:27,639 --> 00:19:30,631
The rose I went to the trouble
of bringing was a waste.

246
00:19:31,576 --> 00:19:33,237
My narcissus too...

247
00:19:36,948 --> 00:19:38,916
Oh... How boring.

248
00:19:39,617 --> 00:19:40,914
Hey, Naruto!

249
00:19:41,119 --> 00:19:45,579
The swimsuit gals have gone,
so why don't we call it a day?

250
00:19:45,790 --> 00:19:47,883
What? Let's stay a little longer!

251
00:19:48,026 --> 00:19:50,221
Come on, a little longer...
Just a little longer!

252
00:19:50,361 --> 00:19:54,593
I'm hungry. And I'm pretty tired too.

253
00:19:54,933 --> 00:19:56,491
You haven't even done anything.

254
00:19:56,634 --> 00:20:00,161
You should be thankful
I hung out with you!

255
00:20:00,672 --> 00:20:02,139
<i>He's getting ticked off at me.</i>

256
00:20:03,107 --> 00:20:06,270
